            BUILD. build/curves.js (Table 4-34 constants, family id `ge850-ieee` so it can never be
            confused with another vendor's "IEEE" curves), build/engine.js (trip, reset, interval,
            overlap), verify/published.js (the 210 cell answer key, GENERATED from the PDF, not typed),
